{"id":303716,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-陕西省神木县数千民众集会阻止县委书记/","date":"2013-07-15T09:17:54Z","modified":"2013-07-15T09:17:54Z","title":"维权网 | 陕西省神木县数千民众集会阻止县委书记离任（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日上午，数千民众聚集在陕西省榆林市神木县政府大门口，因为有消息说神木县书记雷正西调离，几天来神木网友通过微信、微博互相传递雷正西贪污腐败之事，并约定</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日上午在县政府前广场集会，不让他走。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当地政府出动大量警察、特警，集会现场有十余人遭到抓捕，另有数人因为手机拍照被带离。民众集会期间，一直呼喊雷正西出来，但雷正西始终没有露面。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><span>神木县委书记雷正西在当政期间，神木经济一落千丈，前任书记为神木留下的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span>亿元人民币的财政盈余，而现在却负债</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>亿，神木当地的民间借贷资金链断裂，当地许多人损失惨重，但是雷正西对此却毫无作为。另外据当地民众提供的消息，作为一个追求完成</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GDP</span><span>指标以便获得高位的县委书记，因为近来的经济情况不好，雷正西居然动用十几个亿的县财政款项来填补</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GDP</span><span>。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5g1RHPhb-qI/UeOiun5NT_I/AAAAAAAAlU4/K1YXns-UgHI/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"280\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-5g1RHPhb-qI/UeOiun5NT_I/AAAAAAAAlU4/K1YXns-UgHI/s400/1.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VCaytZWGKaU/UeOivxAnlhI/AAAAAAAAlVA/X1wWFT58MA0/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VCaytZWGKaU/UeOivxAnlhI/AAAAAAAAlVA/X1wWFT58MA0/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"343\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-tu_frRpzhRA/UeOixeu-S_I/AAAAAAAAlVI/QQwPCcEvhyg/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.b